---
---
<section class="py-24 px-6 relative z-10 bg-white">
  <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-zinc-200 to-transparent"></div>
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 group">
    <div class="md:col-span-5">
      <p class="text-xs font-medium tracking-widest text-zinc-400 uppercase mb-4">Mengapa custom?</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight leading-tight text-zinc-950 transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:translate-x-2">
        Biaya Nyata dari Tools yang Salah
      </h2>

      <!-- Comparison table -->
      <div class="mt-8 overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-zinc-200/60 text-xs">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-4 bg-zinc-50 border-b border-zinc-200/60">
          <div class="p-3 font-medium text-zinc-400"></div>
          <div class="p-3 font-medium text-zinc-500 text-center">Low-Code</div>
          <div class="p-3 font-medium text-zinc-500 text-center">ERP Besar</div>
          <div class="p-3 font-medium text-zinc-950 text-center">Pixelcraft</div>
        </div>
        {[
          ['Fleksibilitas', '❌', '❌', '✅'],
          ['Harga terjangkau', '✅', '❌', '✅'],
          ['Proses lokal', '❌', '❌', '✅'],
          ['Support Bahasa Indonesia', '❌', '❌', '✅'],
        ].map(([label, a, b, c]) => (
          <div class="grid grid-cols-4 border-b border-zinc-100 last:border-0 hover:bg-zinc-50/50 transition-colors">
            <div class="p-3 text-zinc-600 font-medium">{label}</div>
            <div class="p-3 text-center text-zinc-400">{a}</div>
            <div class="p-3 text-center text-zinc-400">{b}</div>
            <div class="p-3 text-center font-medium text-zinc-950">{c}</div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="md:col-span-7 space-y-6 text-base leading-relaxed mt-1 md:mt-0 text-zinc-500 relative">
      <div class="absolute -left-6 top-0 w-1 h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-zinc-200 to-transparent rounded-full transform scale-y-0 group-hover:scale-y-100 transition-transform duration-700 origin-top"></div>
      <p class="transition-all duration-500 group-hover:text-zinc-700">
        Biaya lisensi terlihat jelas. Biaya tersembunyi dari tools yang tidak cocok — tidak.
      </p>
      <p class="transition-all duration-500 delay-75 group-hover:text-zinc-700">
        Low-code terlalu terbatas untuk proses Anda yang kompleks. ERP besar terlalu mahal dan kaku untuk UMKM Indonesia. Pixelcraft ada di tengah: custom tools yang pas di kantong dan benar-benar sesuai proses lokal.
      </p>
      <p class="transition-all duration-500 delay-150 group-hover:text-zinc-700 font-medium text-zinc-600">
        Software custom menghilangkan gap antara cara bisnis Anda bekerja dan cara software Anda bekerja. Investasi awal diimbangi dengan hilangnya workaround, berkurangnya kerja manual, dan meningkatnya keandalan data.
      </p>

      <!-- Grant callout -->
      <div class="mt-2 p-5 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200/60 bg-zinc-50/60 flex gap-4 items-start hover:border-zinc-300 hover:bg-zinc-50 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-9 h-9 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center bg-zinc-100 text-zinc-700 shrink-0 mt-0.5">
          <iconify-icon icon="solar:diploma-linear" class="text-lg" style="stroke-width: 1.5;"></iconify-icon>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-zinc-800 mb-1">Bisa dibantu pakai dana pemerintah</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed">
            Program Making Indonesia 4.0 dan subsidi digitalisasi UMKM bisa menanggung sebagian biaya sistem Anda. Kami bantu proses pengajuannya — gratis.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
